        <briefdescription>
<para>Short Address (in CPU byte order) </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Range:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>0x0000–0xfffd: associated, short address was assigned</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>0xfffe: associated but no short address assigned</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>0xffff: not associated (default),</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>See section 6.4.1, table 6-4 (Usage of the shart address) and section 8.4.3.1, table 8-94, macShortAddress. </para>
